   Instead of using a dodgy proxy try out ZenMate VPN. We never log any of
   our users browsing data so nobody, including us, will know what you are
   doing online. We are committed to helping build a secure, private, and
   free internet.

   Download ZenMate to instantly access your favorite websites. You'll be
